commit.message:
Remove use of reg_mentioned_p.

2009-11-20  Sebastian Pop  <sebastian.pop@amd.com>

	* config/i386/sse.md (*xop_pmacsdql_mem): Don't call reg_mentioned_p.
	(xop_mulv2div2di3_low): Same.
	(*xop_pmacsdqh_mem): Same.

From-SVN: r154399
